    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Scenario 4",
    "long_instructions": "*Review the scenario below and use the AI Chat to learn more in-depth about this threat:*\r\n\r\n## Scenario 4\r\n\r\nIt's the last day to submit college applications to Northfield State, a major university with a large student population. \r\n\r\nThousands of students begin uploading their forms — but suddenly, the site slows to a crawl and eventually crashes.\r\n\r\nStudents panic, unable to submit their applications.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://images.code.org/849e8656a1f40ce463976fc1021a494c-image-1752764919484.08.15 AM.png\" alt=\"computer with message System Down on screen\" width=\"300\"/>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Chat with an Expert: Network Security Engineer\r\n\r\nA **network security engineer** designs, implements, and maintains systems that protect an organization’s network from cyber threats and unauthorized access.\r\n",
    "aichat_settings": {
      "initialCustomizations": {
        "selectedModelId": "gpt-4o-mini",
